## Key Findings
- **Core Purpose**: AI-driven spiritual mentoring for youth retreats with focus on privacy and safety.
- **Tech Stack**: 
  - Backend: Node.js, Express
  - Frontend: Vanilla JS, CSS (in `public/`)
  - AI: Anthropic Claude (Haiku), Groq (Llama/Gemma as fallback)
  - Data: JSON files + Supabase
- **Key Modules**: 
  - `lib/mentors.js`: Defines AI personas.
  - `lib/crisis.js`: Safety monitoring.
  - `lib/anonymize.js`: Privacy protection.
  - `public/teacher/dashboard.html`: Existing analytics dashboard.

## Dashboard Potential
- The existing Teacher Dashboard can be adapted to monitor AI agent performance.
- The "Mentors" system can be expanded to manage specialized task agents.
- The "Insights" system can be used for cross-agent data aggregation.
